        Have questions? We're here to help! Send us a message and we'll respond as soon as possible.
      </p>
      
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/+919895011185"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="group flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full py-3 px-4 bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-600 text-white rounded-xl font-medium transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-emerald-500/30 active:scale-[0.98]"
